  <brief_title>A Phase 3 Evaluation of Daclatasvir and Asunaprevir in Treatment-naive Subjects With Chronic Hepatitis C Genotype 1b Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3 Evaluation of Daclatasvir and Asunaprevir in Treatment-naive Subjects With Chronic Hepatitis C Genotype 1b Infection</official_title>
  <sponsors>
