  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a regimen consisting of daclatasvir and
      asunaprevir is effective in treatment-naive patients with chronic hepatitis genotype 1b
      infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
